<p><a name="Operating_system_support" id="Operating_system_support"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=ATA_over_Ethernet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Operating system support">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Operating system support</span></h2>
