<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.coraid.com/documents/AoEr10.txt" class="external free" title="http://www.coraid.com/documents/AoEr10.txt" rel="nofollow">http://www.coraid.com/documents/AoEr10.txt</a></li>
